ISNULL(rk.KundenReferenz, ''), ISNULL(rk.RO_BestellID, ''), ISNULL(wr.Beschreibung, ''), pos.TerminDatum FROM dbo.VIRTLWARTERAUM vw with(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN dbo.EBENE4 u WITH(NOLOCK) ON u.Ebene1 = vw.Ebene1 AND u.Ebene2 = vw.Ebene2 AND u.Ebene3 = vw.Ebene3 AND u.Ebene4 = vw.Ebene4 LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.WARTERAUM wr WITH(NOLOCK) ON wr.Ebene1 = vw.Ebene1 AND wr.Ebene2 = vw.Ebene2 AND wr.Ebene3 = vw.Ebene3 AND wr.Ebene4 = vw.Ebene4 AND wr.Warteraum_Nr = vw.Warteraum LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.REPARATURKOPF rk with(index(REP_AUFTNR)NOLOCK) ON vw.Ebene1 = rk.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = rk.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = rk.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = rk.Ebene4 AND vw.AUFTNR = rk.AUFTNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.STATUSCODES sc WITH(NOLOCK) ON sc.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND sc.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND sc.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND sc.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND sc.STATUS = rk.Event LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.GERAETE ger with(index(Geraete_IDNR)NOLOCK) ON ger.Ebene1 = rk.Ebene1 AND ger.Ebene2 = rk.Ebene2 AND ger.Ebene3 = rk.Ebene3 AND ger.Ebene4 = rk.Ebene4 AND ger.IDNR = rk.IDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.FEHLERCODE fc WITH(NOLOCK) ON fc.Ebene1 = rk.Ebene1 AND fc.Ebene2 = rk.Ebene2 AND fc.Ebene3 = rk.Ebene3 AND fc.Ebene4 = rk.Ebene4 AND fc.Code = rk.Fehlercode AND fc.Art = 'S' LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.MITARBEITER ma WITH(NOLOCK) ON ma.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND ma.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND ma.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND ma.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND ma.MitarbNr = vw.TKNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.MITARBEITER mi WITH(NOLOCK) ON mi.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND mi.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND mi.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND mi.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND mi.MitarbNr = vw.TKNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.HOTLINE ht with(index(HOTLINE_JOBNR)NOLOCK) ON vw.Ebene1 = ht.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = ht.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = ht.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = ht.Ebene4 AND vw.AUFTNR = ht.lfd_Job_Nr LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.GERAETE geh with(index(Geraete_IDNR)NOLOCK) ON geh.Ebene1 = ht.Ebene1 AND geh.Ebene2 = ht.Ebene2 AND geh.Ebene3 = ht.Ebene3 AND geh.Ebene4 = ht.Ebene4 AND geh.IDNR = ht.IDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.GRUND_UNVOLLST uv WITH(NOLOCK) ON rk.Ebene1 = uv.Ebene1 AND rk.Ebene2 = uv.Ebene2 AND rk.Ebene3 = uv.Ebene3 AND rk.Ebene4 = uv.Ebene4 AND rk.grundunvollstaendig = uv.GrundKurz LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN kd WITH (INDEX(KUNDEN_KDNR)NOLOCK) ON ( CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE rk.Ebene1 END) = kd.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE rk.Ebene2 END) = kd.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE rk.Ebene3 END ) = kd.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE rk.Ebene4 END) = kd.Ebene4 AND rk.Kunden_Nr = kd.KDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN kh WITH (INDEX(KUNDEN_KDNR)NOLOCK) ON (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE ht.Ebene1 END) = kh.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE ht.Ebene2 END) = kh.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE ht.Ebene3 END ) = kh.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE ht.Ebene4 END) = kh.Ebene4 AND ht.KundenNr = kh.KDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN btr WITH (INDEX(KUNDEN_KDNR)NOLOCK) ON (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE rk.Ebene1 END ) = btr.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE rk.Ebene2 END) = btr.Ebene2 AND ( CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE rk.Ebene3 END ) = btr.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE rk.Ebene4 END) = btr.Ebene4 AND rk.BKDNR = btr.KDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN hib WITH (INDEX(KUNDEN_KDNR)NOLOCK) ON (CASE WHEN geh.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE geh.Ebene1 END) = hib.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN geh.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE geh.Ebene2 END) = hib.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN geh.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE geh.Ebene3 END) = hib.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN geh.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE geh.Ebene4 END) = hib.Ebene4 AND geh.BETREIBER = hib.KDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.LEANDERSCHLUESSEL lr WITH(NOLOCK) ON lr.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND lr.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND lr.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND lr.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND lr.Laenderschluessel = kd.Laenderschl AND lr.Sprachschluessel = kd.Sprachenschlssell LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.LEANDERSCHLUESSEL lh WITH(NOLOCK) ON lh.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND lh.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND lh.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND lh.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND lh.Laenderschluessel = kh.Laenderschl AND lh.Sprachschluessel = kh.Sprachenschlssell LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.FLS_GEOCODE_ERGEBNIS f WITH(NOLOCK) ON vw.Ebene1 = f.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = f.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = f.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = f.Ebene4 AND f.KDNR = 0 AND f.ErgebnisNummer = vw.AUFTNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.REPARATURKOPF_SLA sla ON vw.Ebene1 = sla.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = sla.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = sla.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = sla.Ebene4 AND vw.AUFTNR = sla.AUFTNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.SERVICEAUFTRAG_PRIORITAET spa ON vw.Ebene1 = spa.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = spa.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = spa.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = spa.Ebene4 AND rk.ServicePrioritaet = spa.Prioritaet LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.VERKETTUNG_WWS_REP wwrep on vw.Ebene1=wwrep.Ebene1 and vw.Ebene2=wwrep.Ebene2 and vw.Ebene3=wwrep.Ebene3 and vw.Ebene4=wwrep.Ebene4 and vw.AUFTNR=wwrep.REPAuftrags_Nr LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.positionen pos with(index(Positionen_AUFTNR_POSNR)) on vw.Ebene1=pos.Ebene1 and vw.Ebene2=pos.Ebene2 and vw.Ebene3=pos.Ebene3 and vw.Ebene4=pos.Ebene4 and wwrep.WWAuftrags_Nr=pos.AUFTNR and wwrep.Zeilen_Nr=pos.POSNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.NIEDERLASSUNG_KUNDEN ndl_rk with(index(NIEDERLASSUNG_KUNDEN_NDL)) ON ( CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE rk.Ebene1 END) = ndl_rk.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE rk.Ebene2 END) = ndl_rk.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE rk.Ebene3 END ) = ndl_rk.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE rk.Ebene4 END) = ndl_rk.Ebene4 AND ndl_rk.Niederlassung_nr=:5 AND rk.Kunden_Nr = ndl_rk.Kunden_Nr LEFT OUTER JOIN NIEDERLASSUNG_KUNDEN ndl_ht with(index(NIEDERLASSUNG_KUNDEN_NDL)) ON (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE ht.Ebene1 END) = ndl_ht.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE ht.Ebene2 END) = ndl_ht.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE ht.Ebene3 END ) = ndl_ht.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE ht.Ebene4 END) = ndl_ht.Ebene4 AND ndl_ht.Niederlassung_Nr=:5 AND ht.KundenNr = ndl_ht.Kunden_Nr
WHERE vw.Ebene1 = :1 AND vw.Ebene2 = :2 AND vw.Ebene3 = :3 AND vw.Ebene4 = :4 and wr.Planung = 1 and (wr.Bereich = 'H' OR wr.Bereich = 'S')

SELECT vw.AUFTNR ,rk.BStrasse ,rk.BOrt ,rk.Fehlercode ,vw.Modell ,rk.Event ,rk.Prioritaet ,vw.TKNR, rk.Entfernung ,vw.Fahrtzeit ,vw.Termin_Datum ,vw.Termin_Zeit ,vw.Dauer ,vw.Reaktionszeit_Datum ,vw.Reaktionszeit_bis, vw.Ebene1 ,vw.Ebene2 ,vw.Ebene3 ,vw.Ebene4 ,ht.lfd_Job_Nr ,ht.Strasse AS HotStrasse ,ht.Ort ,ht.Rufcode, 2 AS htevent ,CONVERT(SMALLINT, ht.Prioritaet) AS htprio ,ht.letzterMitarbeiter ,sc.Beschreibung ,rk.BName_I, rk.BName_II ,rk.BName_III ,ht.Name_1 ,ht.Name_2 ,ht.Name_3 ,ht.Strasse ,ht.PLZ ,ht.Ort AS HotOrt ,rk.IDNR, ht.IDNR AS HotIDNR ,ger.ModellNummer ,ht.Modell AS HotModell ,rk.SNR ,ht.Seriennummer ,rk.Klartext_char, fc.[TEXT] ,ht.Stichwort ,ma.Name AS MitarbeiterName ,mi.Name AS HotlineMirarbName ,vw.Warteraum ,rk.Datum ,rk.Zeit, ht.Rufeingang_Datum ,ht.Rufeingang_Zeit ,rk.Bemerkung ,ger.Artikelnummer ,rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf, ISNULL(ht.ZentralerKunde, 0) AS ZentralerKunde_Hot ,rk.Kunden_Nr ,ht.KundenNr ,wr.Bereich ,rk.BKDNR, rk.ZentralerBetreiber ,uv.GrundBeschreibung ,geh.BETREIBER ,ISNULL(geh.ZentralerBetreiber, 0) AS ZentralerBetreiber_HotGer, rk.VorOrtZeit ,rk.VorOrtZeitDatum, (SELECT TOP (1) FolgeAuftrag FROM dbo.AUFTRAGVERFOLGUNG as av WITH(NOLOCK,index(AUFTRAGVERFOLGUNG_UNTER)) WHERE (Ebene1 = vw.Ebene1) AND (Ebene2 = vw.Ebene2) AND (Ebene3 = vw.Ebene3) AND (Ebene4 = vw.Ebene4) AND (FolgeAuftrag = vw.AUFTNR)) AS Verfolgung, kd.Matchcode AS Matchcode_Service, kd.Laenderschl, kd.Sprachenschlssell, kd.ServiceBenachrichtigung, kd.SerBenAusNEU, kd.SerBenAusSTATUS, kd.SerBenAusABSCHLUSS, kh.Matchcode AS Matchcode_Hotline, kh.Laenderschl AS Laenderschl_hot, kh.Sprachenschlssell AS Sprachenschl_hot, kh.ServiceBenachrichtigung AS ServiceBen_hot, kh.SerBenAusNEU AS SerBenNEU_hot, kh.SerBenAusSTATUS AS SerBenSTATUS_hot, kh.SerBenAusABSCHLUSS AS SerBenABSCHLUSS_hot, isnull(ndl_ht.keineAnzeige, 0) AS keinAnzeigeHotline, btr.Matchcode AS Matchcode_Btreiber, btr.Laenderschl AS Laenderschl_Btr, btr.Sprachenschlssell AS Sprachenschl_btr, btr.ServiceBenachrichtigung AS ServiceBen_btr, btr.SerBenAusNEU AS SerBenNEU_btr, btr.SerBenAusSTATUS AS SerBenSTATUS_Btr, btr.SerBenAusABSCHLUSS AS SerBenABSCHLUSS_btr, hib.Matchcode AS Matchcode_HotIDNR, hib.Laenderschl AS Laenderschl_HotIDNRr, hib.Sprachenschlssell AS Sprachenschl_HotIDNR, hib.ServiceBenachrichtigung AS ServiceBen_HotIDNR, hib.SerBenAusNEU AS SerBenNEU__HotIDNR, hib.SerBenAusSTATUS AS SerBenSTATUS_HotIDNR, hib.SerBenAusABSCHLUSS AS SerBenABSCHLUSS_HotIDNR, isnull(ndl_rk.keineAnzeige,0) AS keinAnzeigeReparatur, lr.PLZPicture, lh.PLZPicture AS PLZPictureHot, rk.BPLZ AS RepPLZ, f.Ergebnistext, sla.VorOrtGehalten, sla.ISTVorOrtZeitDatum, sla.ISTVorOrtZeit, sla.WiederherstellungDatum, sla.WiederherstellungZeit, ISNULL(spa.ExterneBeschreibung, '') AS Prio, ISNULL(spa.Beschreibung, '') AS PrioBeschreibung, ISNULL(rk.KundenReferenz, '') AS KundenReferenz, ISNULL(rk.RO_BestellID, '') AS RO_BestellID, ISNULL(wr.Beschreibung, '') AS WRBeschreibung, pos.TerminDatum FROM dbo.VIRTLWARTERAUM AS vw with(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN dbo.EBENE4 AS u WITH(NOLOCK) ON u.Ebene1 = vw.Ebene1 AND u.Ebene2 = vw.Ebene2 AND u.Ebene3 = vw.Ebene3 AND u.Ebene4 = vw.Ebene4 LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.WARTERAUM AS wr WITH(NOLOCK) ON wr.Ebene1 = vw.Ebene1 AND wr.Ebene2 = vw.Ebene2 AND wr.Ebene3 = vw.Ebene3 AND wr.Ebene4 = vw.Ebene4 AND wr.Warteraum_Nr = vw.Warteraum LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.REPARATURKOPF AS rk with(index(REP_AUFTNR)NOLOCK) ON vw.Ebene1 = rk.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = rk.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = rk.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = rk.Ebene4 AND vw.AUFTNR = rk.AUFTNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.STATUSCODES AS sc WITH(NOLOCK) ON sc.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND sc.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND sc.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND sc.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND sc.STATUS = rk.Event LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.GERAETE AS ger with(index(Geraete_IDNR)NOLOCK) ON ger.Ebene1 = rk.Ebene1 AND ger.Ebene2 = rk.Ebene2 AND ger.Ebene3 = rk.Ebene3 AND ger.Ebene4 = rk.Ebene4 AND ger.IDNR = rk.IDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.FEHLERCODE AS fc WITH(NOLOCK) ON fc.Ebene1 = rk.Ebene1 AND fc.Ebene2 = rk.Ebene2 AND fc.Ebene3 = rk.Ebene3 AND fc.Ebene4 = rk.Ebene4 AND fc.Code = rk.Fehlercode AND fc.Art = 'S' LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.MITARBEITER AS ma WITH(NOLOCK) ON ma.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND ma.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND ma.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND ma.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND ma.MitarbNr = vw.TKNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.MITARBEITER AS mi WITH(NOLOCK) ON mi.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND mi.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND mi.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND mi.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND mi.MitarbNr = vw.TKNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.HOTLINE AS ht with(index(HOTLINE_JOBNR)NOLOCK) ON vw.Ebene1 = ht.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = ht.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = ht.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = ht.Ebene4 AND vw.AUFTNR = ht.lfd_Job_Nr LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.GERAETE AS geh with(index(Geraete_IDNR)NOLOCK) ON geh.Ebene1 = ht.Ebene1 AND geh.Ebene2 = ht.Ebene2 AND geh.Ebene3 = ht.Ebene3 AND geh.Ebene4 = ht.Ebene4 AND geh.IDNR = ht.IDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.GRUND_UNVOLLST AS uv WITH(NOLOCK) ON rk.Ebene1 = uv.Ebene1 AND rk.Ebene2 = uv.Ebene2 AND rk.Ebene3 = uv.Ebene3 AND rk.Ebene4 = uv.Ebene4 AND rk.grundunvollstaendig = uv.GrundKurz LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN AS kd WITH (INDEX(KUNDEN_KDNR)NOLOCK) ON ( CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE rk.Ebene1 END) = kd.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE rk.Ebene2 END) = kd.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE rk.Ebene3 END ) = kd.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE rk.Ebene4 END) = kd.Ebene4 AND rk.Kunden_Nr = kd.KDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN AS kh WITH (INDEX(KUNDEN_KDNR)NOLOCK) ON (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE ht.Ebene1 END) = kh.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE ht.Ebene2 END) = kh.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE ht.Ebene3 END ) = kh.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE ht.Ebene4 END) = kh.Ebene4 AND ht.KundenNr = kh.KDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN AS btr WITH (INDEX(KUNDEN_KDNR)NOLOCK) ON (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE rk.Ebene1 END ) = btr.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE rk.Ebene2 END) = btr.Ebene2 AND ( CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE rk.Ebene3 END ) = btr.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE rk.Ebene4 END) = btr.Ebene4 AND rk.BKDNR = btr.KDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.KUNDEN AS hib WITH (INDEX(KUNDEN_KDNR)NOLOCK) ON (CASE WHEN geh.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE geh.Ebene1 END) = hib.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN geh.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE geh.Ebene2 END) = hib.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN geh.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE geh.Ebene3 END) = hib.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN geh.ZentralerBetreiber = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE geh.Ebene4 END) = hib.Ebene4 AND geh.BETREIBER = hib.KDNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.LEANDERSCHLUESSEL AS lr WITH(NOLOCK) ON lr.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND lr.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND lr.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND lr.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND lr.Laenderschluessel = kd.Laenderschl AND lr.Sprachschluessel = kd.Sprachenschlssell LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.LEANDERSCHLUESSEL AS lh WITH(NOLOCK) ON lh.Ebene1 = u.ZentralEbene1 AND lh.Ebene2 = u.ZentralEbene2 AND lh.Ebene3 = u.ZentralEbene3 AND lh.Ebene4 = u.ZentralEbene4 AND lh.Laenderschluessel = kh.Laenderschl AND lh.Sprachschluessel = kh.Sprachenschlssell LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.FLS_GEOCODE_ERGEBNIS AS f WITH(NOLOCK) ON vw.Ebene1 = f.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = f.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = f.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = f.Ebene4 AND f.KDNR = 0 AND f.ErgebnisNummer = vw.AUFTNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.REPARATURKOPF_SLA AS sla WITH(NOLOCK) ON vw.Ebene1 = sla.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = sla.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = sla.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = sla.Ebene4 AND vw.AUFTNR = sla.AUFTNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.SERVICEAUFTRAG_PRIORITAET AS spa WITH(NOLOCK) ON vw.Ebene1 = spa.Ebene1 AND vw.Ebene2 = spa.Ebene2 AND vw.Ebene3 = spa.Ebene3 AND vw.Ebene4 = spa.Ebene4 AND rk.ServicePrioritaet = spa.Prioritaet LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.VERKETTUNG_WWS_REP as wwrep WITH(NOLOCK) on vw.Ebene1=wwrep.Ebene1 and vw.Ebene2=wwrep.Ebene2 and vw.Ebene3=wwrep.Ebene3 and vw.Ebene4=wwrep.Ebene4 and vw.AUFTNR=wwrep.REPAuftrags_Nr LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.positionen as pos with(index(Positionen_AUFTNR_POSNR)NOLOCK) on vw.Ebene1=pos.Ebene1 and vw.Ebene2=pos.Ebene2 and vw.Ebene3=pos.Ebene3 and vw.Ebene4=pos.Ebene4 and wwrep.WWAuftrags_Nr=pos.AUFTNR and wwrep.Zeilen_Nr=pos.POSNR LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.NIEDERLASSUNG_KUNDEN ndl_rk with(index(NIEDERLASSUNG_KUNDEN_NDL)NOLOCK) ON ( CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE rk.Ebene1 END) = ndl_rk.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE rk.Ebene2 END) = ndl_rk.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE rk.Ebene3 END ) = ndl_rk.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN rk.ZentralerRechnEmpf = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE rk.Ebene4 END) = ndl_rk.Ebene4 AND ndl_rk.Niederlassung_nr=:5 AND rk.Kunden_Nr = ndl_rk.Kunden_Nr LEFT OUTER JOIN NIEDERLASSUNG_KUNDEN ndl_ht with(index(NIEDERLASSUNG_KUNDEN_NDL)NOLOCK) ON (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene1 ELSE ht.Ebene1 END) = ndl_ht.Ebene1 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene2 ELSE ht.Ebene2 END) = ndl_ht.Ebene2 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene3 ELSE ht.Ebene3 END ) = ndl_ht.Ebene3 AND (CASE WHEN ht.ZentralerKunde = 1 THEN U.ZentralEbene4 ELSE ht.Ebene4 END) = ndl_ht.Ebene4 AND ndl_ht.Niederlassung_Nr=:5 AND ht.KundenNr = ndl_ht.Kunden_Nr

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT A.MitarbNr,A.Name,case when b.GruppePlanung>0 then b.GruppePlanung else a.GruppePlanung end as Gruppe FROM MITARBEITER A WITH(NOLOCK), TEAM_TECHNIKER B WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE A.Ebene1 = :1 AND A.Ebene2 = :2 AND A.Ebene3 = :3 AND A.Ebene4 = :4 AND A.Inaktiv = 0 AND A.Techniker = 1 AND B.Ebene1 = :5 AND B.Ebene2 = :6 AND B.Ebene3 = :7 AND B.Ebene4 = :8 AND B.TEAM = :9 AND B.MITARBEITER = A.MitarbNr ORDER BY A.Ebene1 ASC ,A.Ebene2 ASC ,A.Ebene3 ASC ,A.Ebene4 ASC , Gruppe ASC ,A.MitarbNr ASC
